cleanerRequest.body:
Hello {CleanerName},

We have a new booking for {PropertyName} and need a cleaning and laundry turnover.

Details:
- Date: {Date}
- Time: {Time}
- Address: {Address}
- Estimated Duration: {CleaningDuration}

Are you available on {Date} at {Time} to do a cleaning and laundry turnover at {Address}?

Please reply with "yes" or "no".

Thank you,
{OwnerName}

cleanerConfirmation.body:
Hello {CleanerName},

Thank you for confirming your availability!

Your cleaning appointment has been scheduled:
- Property: {PropertyName}
- Date: {Date}
- Time: {Time}
- Address: {Address}
- Duration: {CleaningDuration}

Access Instructions:
{AccessInstructions}

Special Instructions:
{SpecialInstructions}

A calendar invite has been sent to you separately.

If you have any questions, please contact the property owner.

Thank you,
{OwnerName}

ownerNotification.body:
Hello,

A cleaning has been scheduled for {PropertyName}:

- Cleaner: {CleanerName}
- Date: {Date}
- Time: {Time}
- Address: {Address}

You have been copied on the calendar invite.

Thank you,
{OwnerName}

ownerEscalation.body:
Hello,

We were unable to secure a cleaner for the following booking:

- Property: {PropertyName}
- Check-in Date: {CheckInDate}
- Checkout Date: {CheckoutDate}
- Cleaning Needed: {Date} at {Time}
- Address: {Address}

All {CleanerCount} preferred cleaners were contacted and either declined or did not respond.

Cleaners contacted:
{CleanerList}

Please arrange for cleaning services manually.

Booking Details:
- Platform: {Platform}
- Booking Reference: {BookingReference}
- Guest Name: {GuestName}

Thank you,
{OwnerName}

